165→    expectedFacts: "The observation claims the entire authentication system is fundamentally broken, but no entities are linked as evidence. Without cited evidence, this sweeping claim is unsupported.",
166→  },
167→
168→  // --- Contradiction detection: finds clear contradictions ---
169→  {
170→    id: "detect-contradictions-trpc-vs-rest",
